data.title: Trevecca Announces Dean’s List for Spring 2024 Semester
data.meta_description: Discover the Dean's List honorees at Trevecca Nazarene University for the Spring 2024 semester. See the full list of standout undergraduate students achieving academic excellence.
data.text:
Trevecca Nazarene University has announced its dean’s list honorees for the spring 2024 semester.

To be named to the dean’s list, undergraduates must attain a semester grade point average of 3.50 or higher on a 4.00 grading scale. Traditional undergraduates must be enrolled full-time, while non-traditional undergraduates must have completed 12 or more hours during the academic period.

To share an individual student’s accomplishment with a local newspaper, download the news release template and fill in the information specific to the student (replacing the bracketed placeholders), and then submit the completed document to the news outlet.

The following is a list of the undergraduate students named to the dean’s list, grouped in traditional and nontraditional categories.
